nodes.text: Swamps, also known as marshes, were areas of land which often included thick vegetation and large bodies of water. Planets with areas of swamp land included Artiod Minor, Balnab, Rodia, Naboo, Chal Hudda, Dagobah, Galagolos V, Indoumodo, Kinrah, Marca, Mimban, Mydasos, Nal Hutta, Patitite Pattuna, Ques, Toydaria, Twon Ketee, Graf-World, and Vodran.
